data.description: Nestled within the charming community of Hastings, MN, awaits an extraordinary family home that effortlessly connects sophistication with everyday comfort. A 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom modern built in 2012, designed to elevate your lifestyle. Features an open concept living room and kitchen. This is your opportunity to own an exceptional residence in Hastings, MN, where modern luxury meets family comfort. Still feels new and in close proximity to many points of interest.
